The,Noodlio,Pay,API,simplifies,the,integration,of,payments,acceptance,portals,in,websites,and,apps,Its,RESTful,architecture,allows,apps,to,initiate,instant,API,requests,for,validating,input,data,and,applying,charges,on,purchases,made,on,a,website,The,API,uses,Stripe,to,expedite,the,instantaneous,transfer,of,funds,to,destination,accounts,It,sends,requests,in,JSON,or,HTTP,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format